            <title>[THRIFT-2278] Buffered transport doesn&apos;t support writes &gt; buffer size</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2278</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
